Package: consprio
Type: Package
Title: Conservation Priority Index
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anthony Basooma
Maintainer: Anthony Basooma <bas4ster@gmail.com>
Description: The packages allows to prioritise the selection of waterbodies or habitats
    for conservation and management based on the species composition, the surface area of 
    the waterbody or habitat, the endemeicity or rarenes of the species among or betweeen
    the waterbodies or habitats in question, and IUCN conservation status for all the 
    species considered in particular.
